  "title": "Warm Resinous Algerian Fruit Tagine",
  "description": "A sweet and savory Algerian dish featuring powdered sugar and a variety of fruits, served in a stone bowl, perfect for a crowd, this vegetarian friendly recipe is a real crowd pleaser",
