  "instructions": [
    "Heat the honey in a saucepan over low heat until it is warm and runny.",
    "Add the chopped dried apricots, prunes, lemon juice, and orange blossom water to the saucepan and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 10 minutes, or until the fruit is tender.",
    "Stir in the powdered sugar until it is dissolved.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a stone bowl and top with sliced almonds and raisins.",
    "Serve the tagine warm, garnished with additional powdered sugar if desired."
  ],
